To further understand the biological functions of these DEGs, GO enrichment analysis of three categories, including biological process (BP), cellular component (CC) and molecular function (MF) were performed using the Database for Annotation, Visualization and Integrated Discovery (DAVID; version 6.8, URL: 

  https://david.ncifcrf.gov/
 ). KEGG pathway analysis was conducted using the KOBAS database (version 3.0, URL: 

  http://kobas.cbi.pku.edu.cn/
 ). False discovery rate (FDR) <0.05 was considered to be of statistical significance.
